text: Farrer Park MRT Station (NE8) is an underground station along the North East Line of the Mass Rapid Transit at the boundary of Kallang and Rochor planning areas, Singapore. It is at the north end of the ethnic neighbourhood of Little India. This station is near Mustafa Centre, Serangoon Plaza, and City Square Mall. ==References== Category:Mass Rapid Transit (Singapore) stations
title: Farrer Park MRT station
